sentences: Fish Leong (simplified Chinese: 梁静茹; traditional Chinese: 梁靜茹; pinyin: Liáng Jìngrú, born 16 June 1978) is a Malaysian singer.
She debuted her singing career in Taiwan and signed to Rock Records in October 1997.
Her debut album, Grown Up Overnight, was released in September 1999, but had many promotions cancelled due to 921 earthquake.

In February 2010, Leong married Taiwanese wine merchant Tony Chao in Boracay, Philippines, and their child Anderson Chao was born in April 2014.
